# Yogurt Panna Cotta with Walnuts and Honey

Based on [Yogurt Panna Cotta with Walnuts and Honey - Smitten Kitchen](https://smittenkitchen.com/2013/04/yogurt-panna-cotta-with-walnuts-and-honey) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251119191555/https://smittenkitchen.com/2013/04/yogurt-panna-cotta-with-walnuts-and-honey/))

